        "parameters": {
          "color": 6,
          "width": 560,
          "height": 660,
          "content": "# 2. Google Sheets Whitelist Config\n\n## To filter contacts against a whitelist:\n### 1. Make a copy of [this spreadsheet]({{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }}\n**OR** create a Google Sheet with two columns:\n| **email**     | **company**      |\n\n\n### 2. Add whitelisted emails and their company as rows in the sheet and configure this node **Document** and **Sheet** to point to it.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"
